com.lsc.ctesterfx.logger

Class Printer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lsc.ctesterfx.logger.AbstractLogger
      • com.lsc.ctesterfx.logger.Printer

  • public class Printer
extends AbstractLogger
    Class that logs the results in the output panel. There's only one panel, so only one instance of Printer is forced with a Singleton. The MainController is responsible of setting this up once.
    Author:
    dma@logossmartcard.com
